ZH: 我们需要清理这个房间。
EN: We need to clean up this room.

ZH: 帮我清理一下办公桌。
EN: Help me tidy up the office desk.

ZH: 我们每年春天都会清理花园。
EN: We clean the garden every spring.

ZH: 他在清理冰箱时不小心打翻了一罐果汁。
EN: He accidentally spilled a can of juice while cleaning the fridge.

ZH: 妈妈昨天忙着清理厨房，所以没时间做晚饭。
EN: Mom was too busy cleaning the kitchen yesterday to make dinner.

ZH: 请清理好自己的座位，然后离开餐桌。
EN: Please clean up your seat before leaving the dining table.

ZH: 我们需要雇佣清洁工帮忙清理这个办公室。
EN: We need to hire a cleaner to help clean up this office.

ZH: 请务必清理好玻璃桌面。
EN: Please make sure to clean the glass tabletop.

ZH: 昨晚我花了两个小时清理我的卧室。
EN: I spent two hours cleaning my bedroom last night.

ZH: 他每周都会花时间清理家里的浴室。
EN: He spends time cleaning the bathroom in his house every week.

ZH: 清理这个浴室需要投入更多的时间和精力。
EN: Cleaning this bathroom requires more time and effort.

ZH: 我们需要清理地板上的灰尘。
EN: We need to clean the dust off the floor.

ZH: 请确保清理垃圾桶及时。
EN: Please make sure to clean the trash bin regularly.

ZH: 我们需要清理掉病毒和恶意软件。
EN: We need to clean out viruses and malicious software.

ZH: 他专门负责清理社区公共场所的垃圾。
EN: He is responsible for cleaning up the trash in public areas of the community.

ZH: 我们的垃圾车每周都会来清理一次。
EN: Our garbage truck comes to clean up once a week.

ZH: 请按照指示清理书房内的书架。
EN: Please follow the instructions to clean the bookshelves in the study.

ZH: 这位清洁工每天早上都会来清理办公室。
EN: The cleaner comes to clean the office every morning.

ZH: 清理是保持卫生和健康的重要步骤。
EN: Cleaning is an important step in maintaining hygiene and health.
